"4 ounces chorizo, thinly sliced","2 1/2 cups chopped onion","1 cup fat-free, less-sodium chicken broth","1/3 cup packed brown sugar","1/3 cup cider vinegar","1/3 cup bottled chili sauce","1/3 cup dark molasses","2 teaspoons dry mustard","2 teaspoons chipotle chile powder","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon ground cloves","1/4 teaspoon ground allspice","1  (15-ounce) can black beans, rinsed and drained","1  (15-ounce) can kidney beans, rinsed and drained","1  (15-ounce) can pinto beans, rinsed and drained"